Area of Circle
#import math -math is a package I want import in my program....
#after writing this sentences i am able to access all methods available in math
import math
r=5
area=math.pi*r*r
print(area)

Output:
78.53981633974483
   
#another method
from math import pi
r=5
area=math.pi*r*r     #calculating area of circle by using pi*r*r
print(area)   

Output:
78.53981633974483

#another method
from math import pi
r=int(input('Enter radious'))      #accepting radious from user
area=math.pi*r*r
print(area)

